                        CtsLocationAccessService.COMMAND_REQUEST_CELL_INFO_UPDATE);
                assertTrue(cis == null || cis.isEmpty());
            } catch (SecurityException e) {
                // expected
            }
        }, Manifest.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION);
